{"tid":1795402,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍絲打想約各位手足平安夜見","createTime":"2019-12-24T01:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T15:39:53.000Z","uid":233174,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"95718364b1e8aa5f1589cccf0805b15832ffbcf8","tid":1795402,"uid":233174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T01:20:14.000Z","msg":"唔好意思煩左少少又係小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">12.24 平安夜晚，<br />\n我想見到你地每一位手足！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟過得好好，返學出席率優良，無穿無爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近更加夾埋好同學自家製造純天然skin care<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">無添加任何防腐劑化學品嘅潤唇膏、手工皂、handcream</span></ins></strong><br />\n訓左好耐都知<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全港催淚放題，迷霧裏最遠處飄來二噁英</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然聲稱BBQ毒性比tg更高，但<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">眼見唔少手足皮膚出現後遺症</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>真係好希望可以光復一下手足塊臉</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">12.24 平安夜晚，20:00尖沙嘴鐘樓</span></strong></span><br />\n各位手足、小朋友去<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>海港城</strong></span><del>window</del> shopping完<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">就過黎拎份禮物啦</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<del>我唔係遊行呀我派禮物咋</del><br />\n係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">免費派禮物俾手足</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">免費派禮物俾手足</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">免費派禮物俾手足</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（重要嘅事要講三次）<br />\n<br />\n<del>無圖邊敢開post</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kvCFRLH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkvCFRLH.jpg&h=8a756ad7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n部分送出嘅手工皂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/23/190651_356ff30095fe59a15b9ae345bccb4d11.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F23%2F190651_356ff30095fe59a15b9ae345bccb4d11.jpeg&h=936ec748&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">兄弟爬山</span>手工皂，隨機配搭<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>黃到金</strong></span>聖誕包裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SYheWcY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSYheWcY.jpg&h=fb598f36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n或者送俾<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span>到<span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span></strong>屋企人聖誕包裝<br />\n<br />\n聽晚<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">所有野免費，唔收錢<br />\n一蚊都唔收，一毫子都唔收<br />\n唔準俾錢啊啊啊啊啊啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n留返啲錢將來一定有可用之處架知嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有暴徒，只有暴政<br />\n沒有購買，只有送贈</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n今年嘅聖誕其實唔會過得快樂<br />\n<strong><ins>不忘有幾多還押手足喺裏面捱凍受苦<br />\n更不忘有手足離開左我地，以後再無機會過聖誕</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NSc24tY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNSc24tY.jpg&h=c2285945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCredit to Nothing Serious<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/661293557322596/posts/2536123073172959?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F661293557322596%2Fposts%2F2536123073172959%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpohgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=3e76c21e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/661293557322596/posts/2536123073172959?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n相信，手足希望所有人平安無事好好照顧自己<br />\n<strong><ins>繼續堅持信念唔好放棄，等佢地終有歸隊嘅一日<br />\n不辜負佢地犧牲，係對佢地最好嘅回報</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fzjUbcg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfzjUbcg.jpg&h=00545f64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCredit to Stand News 立場新聞<br />\n從初夏至寒冬<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>依場運動無停止過<br />\n我地嘅熱情同樣無停止過</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">平安夜晚，要見到你地<br />\n咁樣先會平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n風雨不會沒了期 終於會等到夢寐<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">寧化飛灰 不作浮塵</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/deg7wOb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdeg7wOb.jpg&h=09f8f34e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1392f754f4d10e7ee1da68af9f6bfc8e7043ba98","tid":1795402,"uid":276691,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T01:24:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f8gWuRa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff8gWuRa.jpg&h=2111842c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77cbbf955e1b46da3363a17c139c7e8486b27082","tid":1795402,"uid":276691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T01:25:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eEhq7C6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeEhq7C6.jpg&h=c2021c98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"438332c596ab6190e6f543262d9fc374feaece46","tid":1795402,"uid":276691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T01:26:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ywSFWwG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FywSFWwG.jpg&h=4f4a2188&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70388d45b1e8655bc81fc52254e0e9347f19e68b","tid":1795402,"uid":276691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T01:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0mPUgxg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0mPUgxg.jpg&h=204bb640&s={SIZE}\" />推"},{"pid":"95722664e290edb3e6009c8bc874fb992497d5cd","tid":1795402,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T01:28:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66ae428f671cb49ed11ad77e2450e06c79a092f1","tid":1795402,"uid":160506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T01:29:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab419e891c97dc2be32a358fbae7b1c288f7886","tid":1795402,"uid":232671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T01:29:40.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"24bd0e268ac748057b00680f161b4440aae7f0d8","tid":1795402,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T01:32:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ad0a13e2f063879cf1a8844168ed88e209b409f","tid":1795402,"uid":2662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T01:32:33.000Z","msg":"